        In one week, there are 7 days.
        So in one week, Claire makes 3 * 7 = 21 egg omelets.
        In four weeks, Claire makes 21 * 4 = 84 egg omelets.
        Since each omelet requires 1 egg, Claire will eat 84 eggs in four weeks.
        Since a dozen is equal to 12, Claire will eat 84 / 12 = 7 dozens of eggs.
